### Describe the problem
Currently, Trial and TrialRunner make ray-tune depend on ray that limit the use of ray-tune.
To make ray-tune capable of running on top of some other execution framework, we suggest to do some code refactoring on ray-tune.

1. add interface TrialExecutor that abstracts the execution of a Trial. 

2. replace the corresponding code in TrialRunner.

3. remove some execute releated function including start/stop/pause/resume from Trial.

